_:Nc85a3130da71402ea1c9765dd2461dc5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Kirstin Gray joined the Government Chemist in 2009. She worked at Leatherhead Food Research Association, before joining <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.lgcgroup.com/\">LGC,</a> a life sciences research and testing company, in 1999. She has more than 20 years’ experience providing analytical services to private and public sector customers.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
